high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the door of the fridge and take out the empty glass, then close the fridge door.
Turn left, walk to the counter across the room, turn left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the empty glass down on the counter on the left of the sink.
Turn around, walk to the wooden table and stand in front of it.
Pick up the empty glass from the wooden table.
Turn right, walk to the sink, and stand in front of the dishwasher next to it.
Place the empty glass down behind the other empty glass on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Take the empty glasses from the fridge and table and put them next to the sink on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Pick up the glass in the fridge.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk forward and turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the glass on the counter.
Turn around and step forward and turn right to face the glass on the table.
Pick up the glass on the table.
Turn right and step forward to face the glass on the counter.
Place the glass behind the first glass on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To move two glasses to the counter beside the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the refrigerator
Take a glass out of the refrigerator
Walk to the kitchen counter
Put the glass on the counter
Walk to the table
Pick up a glass from the table
Walk back to the counter
Put the glass on the counter near the other glass
anns.task_desc: Move two glasses to a kitchen counter
